Happy ANIME-MAY! This month we will be looking at anime adaptions of our favorite comic book characters! Join us as we dive deep into the heart of the Marvel's Anime Universe with a special focus on "Iron Man: Rise of Technovore." In this episode, we dissect the action-packed animated film that follows Tony Stark's journey as Iron Man in Anime form. From battling technologically enhanced foes to exploring the depths of Stark's character development, we unravel the intricate layers of this thrilling adventure. What other heroes can use the anime treatment? Does Iron Man work in this art style? Those questions and more will be answered in this episode of the Major Issues Podcast! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

